00:40:14,801 --> 00:40:20,425
The when it comes to you know, that's why the Green New Deal, by the way, includes those four areas.

510
00:40:20,745 --> 00:40:21,746
It's not by accident.

511
00:40:21,806 --> 00:40:24,328
It's not like the favorite shopping list of the progressives.

