00:42:04,616 --> 00:42:08,958
We want it to be more affordable and more inclusive for everybody.

529
00:42:10,239 --> 00:42:11,500
Higher education is tricky.

530
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:17,223
And I teach in this system, so I'm aware of, so this has to do

531
00:42:18,020 --> 00:42:19,141
